dc_description_s: This data represents recreational trails for Bayfield County in 2021, includes the layers BAYFIELD_TRAILS_2021_ATV, BAYFIELD_TRAILS_2021_ATVROUTE, BAYFIELD_TRAILS_2021_SILENT and BAYFIELD_TRAILS_2021_SNOWMOBILE. [For snowmobile: This layer contains snowmobile trail data in Bayfield County. For Silent: This layer contains Silent Sport walking, biking, skiing, horseback riding, and mushing trails in Bayfield County. For ATV Route: This layer contains ATV road routes in Bayfield County. For ATV: This layer contains ATV trail data in Bayfield County. Link to metadata information: https://www.bayfieldcounty.wi.gov/437/GIS-Metadata]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.bayfieldcounty.wi.gov/892/GIS-Data-Access
